<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head><meta charset="utf-8"><meta http-equiv="x-ua-compatible" content="ie=edge"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	<title>Serpent Newsletter Update</title>
	<style type="text/css">* { box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: "Montserrat", "Helvetica", "Inter", -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", "Roboto", "Arial", sans-serif;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      color: #111827;
    }

    table {
      border-collapse: collapse;
      border-spacing: 0;
    }

    img {
      border: 0;
      outline: none;
      text-decoration: none;
      max-width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      display: block;
    }

    a {
      color: inherit;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .newsletter-container {
      width: 100%;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
    }

    .container {
      width: 95%;
      max-width: 960px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .text-center { text-align: center; }
    .rounded-lg { border-radius: 8px; }
    .rounded-md { border-radius: 6px; }
    .rounded-full { border-radius: 9999px; }
    .border { border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; }
    .border-top { border-top: 1px solid #e5eeb; }

    .hero-pill {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      padding: 4px 16px;
      border-radius: 9999px;
      background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 20px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    .gradient-feature {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, hsl(181, 69%, 36%), hsl(181, 69%, 28%));
      color: #f7f7f7;
      border: 1px solid hsl(181, 69%, 36%);
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    .gradient-card {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, hsl(0, 0%, 100%), hsl(181, 20%, 96%));
      border: 1px solid hsl(220, 14%, 90%);
      border-radius: 8px;
      color: hsl(222.2, 84%, 4.9%);
    }

    .gradient-hero {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, hsl(181, 69%, 36%), hsl(181, 69%, 44%));
      border-radius: 8px;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    .muted {
      color: #6b7280;
    }

    .secondary {
      color: hsl(240, 25%, 25%);
    }

    .button-primary {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 24px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      color: hsl(181, 69%, 36%);
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .button-solid {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 12px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      background-color: hsl(181, 69%, 36%);
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 20px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .button-outline {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 12px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      border: 1px solid hsl(220, 14%, 90%);
      background-color: #ffffff;
      color: #111827;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 20px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .cta-note {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 8px;
      padding: 12px 16px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
      background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      font-size: 20px;
      line-height: 28px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    ul {
      margin: 0;
      padding-left: 20px;
    }

    li {
      margin-top: 8px;
    }

    li:first-child {
      margin-top: 0;
    }

    @media only screen and (max-width: 700px) {
      .stack-column,
      .stack-column td {
        display: block !important;
        width: 100% !important;
      }

      .mobile-padding-reset {
        padding-left: 0 !important;
        padding-right: 0 !important;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 34px !important;
        line-height: 1.2 !important;
      }
    }
	</style>
</head>
<body style="height: auto; min-height: auto;">
<div class="newsletter-container">
<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation" width="100%">
	<tbody>
		<tr>
			<td align="center">
			<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="container" role="presentation" width="95%">
				<tbody>
					<tr>
						<td style="padding: 16px 0 0 0;">
						<div class="text-center" style="max-width: 56rem; margin: 16px auto 0 auto;"><span class="hero-pill" style="color:#111827; background-color:#f3f4f6; border-color:#e5e7eb;">Serpent</span>
						<h1 style="margin: 0 auto; max-width: 48rem; font-size: 48px; line-height: 1.1; font-weight: 800; color: #111827;">The all-in-one DevOps platform built for leaders</h1>
						</div>

						<div style="max-width: 100%; margin: 0 auto;">
						<div class="text-center" style="max-width: 56rem; margin: 0 auto 40px auto; padding-top: 24px;">
						<p style="margin: 0; font-size: 18px; line-height: 30px; color:#111827;">We&rsquo;ve just shipped the biggest update to Serpent ever, and it&rsquo;s a game-changer.<br />
						<br />
						Seriously. We tore it down. Rebuilt it. Sanded the edges. Polished the snake.<br />
						<br />
						Now it&rsquo;s faster, smarter, and smoother, <strong>like DevOps butter 🧈 on your Salesforce toast.</strong><br />
						<br />
						You can start a free trial today and book an onboarding demo with us to walk you through your own use case.</p>

						<p style="margin: 24px 0 0 0; font-size: 18px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 600; color:#111827;">Let&rsquo;s dive in 🏊&zwj;♂️</p>
						</div>

						<div style="margin-bottom: 16px;">
						<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="gradient-feature" role="presentation" width="100%">
							<tbody>
								<tr>
									<td style="padding: 24px 24px 12px 24px;">
									<h3 style="margin: 0; font-size: 20px; line-height: 28px; font-weight: 600; color: #f7f7f7;">🎨 Onboarding That Gets You</h3>
									</td>
								</tr>
								<tr>
									<td style="padding: 0 24px 24px 24px;">
									<ul style="font-size:16px; line-height:28px; color:#f7f7f7;">
										<li>Works with scratch orgs, packaging, or something in between</li>
										<li>You&rsquo;ll be up and running before your coffee cools down</li>
										<li>DevOps sherpa guidance included</li>
										<li>No setup-induced migraines</li>
									</ul>
									</td>
								</tr>
							</tbody>
						</table>
						</div>

						<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation" style="margin-bottom:16px;" width="100%">
							<tbody>
								<tr class="stack-column">
									<td class="mobile-padding-reset" style="padding:0 8px 16px 0;" valign="top" width="50%">
									<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="gradient-card" role="presentation" width="100%">
										<tbody>
											<tr>
												<td style="padding:24px 24px 12px 24px;">
												<h3 class="secondary" style="margin:0; font-size:24px; line-height:1.2; font-weight:600;">🚀 Release Without Overhead</h3>
												</td>
											</tr>
											<tr>
												<td style="padding:0 24px 24px 24px;">
												<p style="margin:0 0 12px 0; font-size:18px; line-height:28px; color:gray;">Deploy metadata and data in one flow - no CLI, no scripts.</p>

												<ul class="secondary" style="font-size:16px; line-height:28px;">
													<li>Serpent handles deployments the way Salesforce teams actually work</li>
													<li>Metadata, test data, environments, and rollbacks, all in one place.</li>
													<li>Whether you&rsquo;re releasing a hotfix or promoting a full package, Serpent keeps it simple and reliable, click to deploy, done.</li>
													<li>We even prepare your staging or UAT environment for you, fully synced and ready for testing, so your team can focus on delivery.</li>
												</ul>
												</td>
											</tr>
										</tbody>
									</table>
									</td>
									<td class="mobile-padding-reset" style="padding:0 0 16px 8px;" valign="top" width="50%">
									<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="gradient-card" role="presentation" width="100%">
										<tbody>
											<tr>
												<td style="padding:24px 24px 12px 24px;">
												<h3 class="secondary" style="margin:0; font-size:24px; line-height:1.2; font-weight:600;">🤝 Real-Time Collaboration</h3>
												</td>
											</tr>
											<tr>
												<td style="padding:0 24px 24px 24px;">
												<p style="margin:0 0 12px 0; font-size:18px; line-height:28px; color:gray;">Great releases aren&rsquo;t built in silos.</p>

												<ul class="secondary" style="font-size:16px; line-height:28px;">
													<li>From the first commit to the final deployment, every step is visible, assignable, and accountable all with enterprise ready RBAC.</li>
													<li>A developer wraps up a task. An admin reviews it. A consultant prepares the release. No lost context. No shadow processes. No &ldquo;who touched this last?&rdquo; moments.</li>
													<li>Just seamless handoffs, shared environments, and a single source of truth that keeps everyone moving forward - fast.</li>
												</ul>
												</td>
											</tr>
										</tbody>
									</table>
									</td>
								</tr>
								<tr class="stack-column">
									<td class="mobile-padding-reset" style="padding:0 8px 16px 0;" valign="top" width="50%">
									<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="gradient-card" role="presentation" width="100%">
										<tbody>
											<tr>
												<td style="padding:24px 24px 12px 24px;">
												<h3 class="secondary" style="margin:0; font-size:24px; line-height:1.2; font-weight:600;">♾️ Effortless Salesforce DevOps</h3>
												</td>
											</tr>
											<tr>
												<td style="padding:0 24px 24px 24px;">
												<p style="margin:0 0 12px 0; font-size:18px; line-height:28px; color:gray;">Plan and deploy with confidence - no Git expertise required.</p>

												<ul class="secondary" style="font-size:16px; line-height:28px;">
													<li>Serpent brings GitFlow to life through a clean, task-based UI.</li>
													<li>Each feature, fix, or release is mapped to a task, so teams can work in parallel, track changes clearly, and deploy in controlled stages.</li>
													<li>Every task includes a complete visual history, from development to deployment, providing a built-in audit trail for compliance and accountability.</li>
												</ul>
												</td>
											</tr>
										</tbody>
									</table>
									</td>
									<td class="mobile-padding-reset" style="padding:0 0 16px 8px;" valign="top" width="50%">
									<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="gradient-card" role="presentation" width="100%">
										<tbody>
											<tr>
												<td style="padding:24px 24px 12px 24px;">
												<h3 class="secondary" style="margin:0; font-size:24px; line-height:1.2; font-weight:600;">🔄 Automation for Everyone</h3>
												</td>
											</tr>
											<tr>
												<td style="padding:0 24px 24px 24px;">
												<p style="margin:0 0 12px 0; font-size:18px; line-height:28px; color:gray;">CI/CD that works out of the box - no DevOps team needed.</p>

												<ul class="secondary" style="font-size:16px; line-height:28px;">
													<li>Build automated pipelines without writing a single script.</li>
													<li>Run tests, validate changes, spin up environments, or schedule deployments with just a few clicks.</li>
													<li>Serpent makes automation accessible to your whole team, not just your senior developers.</li>
												</ul>
												</td>
											</tr>
										</tbody>
									</table>
									</td>
								</tr>
								<tr class="stack-column">
									<td class="mobile-padding-reset" style="padding:0 8px 16px 0;" valign="top" width="50%">
									<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="gradient-card" role="presentation" width="100%">
										<tbody>
											<tr>
												<td style="padding:24px 24px 12px 24px;">
												<h3 class="secondary" style="margin:0; font-size:24px; line-height:1.2; font-weight:600;">🏢 Org Management Made Simple</h3>
												</td>
											</tr>
											<tr>
												<td style="padding:0 24px 24px 24px;">
												<p style="margin:0 0 12px 0; font-size:18px; line-height:28px; color:gray;">Connect, manage, and deploy to any Salesforce org - fast.</p>

												<ul class="secondary" style="font-size:16px; line-height:28px;">
													<li>Spin up scratch orgs or connect to existing sandboxes and production with a single click.</li>
													<li>Serpent&rsquo;s org pooling gives your team instant access to ready-to-use environments, helping you test, demo, and deliver without waiting on setup or DevOps overhead.</li>
												</ul>
												</td>
											</tr>
										</tbody>
									</table>
									</td>
									<td class="mobile-padding-reset" style="padding:0 0 16px 8px;" valign="top" width="50%">
									<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="gradient-card" role="presentation" width="100%">
										<tbody>
											<tr>
												<td style="padding:24px 24px 12px 24px;">
												<h3 class="secondary" style="margin:0; font-size:24px; line-height:1.2; font-weight:600;">👨&zwj;💻 VS Code Extension</h3>
												</td>
											</tr>
											<tr>
												<td style="padding:0 24px 24px 24px;">
												<p style="margin:0 0 12px 0; font-size:18px; line-height:28px; color:gray;">Keep coding your way</p>

												<ul class="secondary" style="font-size:16px; line-height:28px;">
													<li>Use VS Code as usual, and Serpent will take care of syncing changes, linking them to the right task, and handling the Git flow in the background.</li>
													<li>No need to switch tools or remember CLI commands&mdash;just focus on writing clean Apex, LWC, and configs.</li>
												</ul>
												</td>
											</tr>
										</tbody>
									</table>
									</td>
								</tr>
							</tbody>
						</table>

						<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="gradient-hero" role="presentation" width="100%">
							<tbody>
								<tr>
									<td align="center" style="padding:32px;">
									<h3 style="margin:0 0 16px 0; font-size:24px; line-height:32px; font-weight:700; color:#ffffff;">TL;DR?</h3>

									<p style="margin:0 0 12px 0; font-size:18px; line-height:28px; color:#ffffff;">Serpent helps you move fast without breaking things, streamlining workflows, reducing deployment friction, and simplifying release cycles so you can ship with confidence and scale smarter.</p>

									<p style="margin:0 0 24px 0; font-size:18px; line-height:28px; color:#ffffff;">Now is the time to test yourself<br />
