									For every Salesforce dev who&rsquo;s ever yelled, &ldquo;WHY did it fail this time?!&rdquo;</p>

									<div style="margin-bottom:24px;"><a class="button-primary" href="https://serpent.tekunda.com">🎁 Start your free trial today</a></div>

									<p class="cta-note">✨ Let&rsquo;s make your next Salesforce releases actually feel good.</p>
									</td>
								</tr>
